{"tid":2428101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國國務院報告批評美國抗疫不力","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T15:39:50.000Z","uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0101c0a6325b362c81f6076c1f9d48131f7aeb","tid":2428101,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中國國務院的2020年美國侵犯人權報告，批評美國在全球需要團結抗疫的時刻，推行單邊主義，成為全球安全與穩定的最大麻煩製造者。<br />\n<br />\n新華社引述報告指，華府在應對新冠疫情方面任性妄為，導致失控，令逾50萬美國人染疫死亡，而疫情失控導致大規模失業潮，貧富差距加速擴大。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指，美國民主制度失序，進一步撕裂社會，選舉成為富人階層「獨角戲」，當地少數族裔遭受系統性種族歧視，社會持續動盪威脅公眾安全，去年槍擊事件數字創歷史新高，造成逾4萬1千人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n對於海外，報告批評美國執意奉行本國優先政策，揮舞制裁大棒，霸淩威脅國際機構。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=425761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425761&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt12yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=777d91a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425761&h=1f679b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=425761</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714fac48762e41b204bbbf982042f06d96538ab2","tid":2428101,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"一講中國屌美國，一個引號就見唔到，Now真係愛國愛黨既電視台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926e3fec437c681ad0e444ea302e34e6d5b02bc4","tid":2428101,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"試下訪問美國人，有幾多人想移民返大陸，調反轉年年都咁多中國人移民出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}